<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>我的客戶紀錄 - Xolair MMP</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header', { user }) %>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="toolbar">
      <label style="font-size:0.9rem; color:#6b7684;">填寫月份：</label>
      <select id="monthSelect"></select>
    </div>
    <div class="layout-2col">
      <div>
        <div class="toolbar">
          <input type="text" id="searchBox" placeholder="搜尋客戶/醫師姓名...">
        </div>
        <div id="customerList"></div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="card" id="formCard" style="display:none;">
          <h2 id="formTitle" style="margin-top:0;"></h2>
          <div style="color:#6b7684; font-size:0.85rem; margin-bottom:1rem;" id="formSubtitle"></div>
          <div class="hint" id="carriedOverHint" style="display:none; text-align:left; background:#fff8e1; color:#8a6d1f; padding:0.6rem 0.8rem; border-radius:6px; margin-bottom:1rem;"></div>
          <form id="recordForm">
            <div class="form-grid">
              <div class="field">
                <label>Team</label>
                <input type="text" name="team">
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label>Customer Tier</label>
                <input type="text" name="customer_tier">
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label>HCP Tier</label>
                <input type="text" name="hcp_tier">
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label>Customer Relationship</label>
                <select name="customer_relationship" data-options="customer_relationship"></select>
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label>Adoption Ladder</label>
                <select name="adoption_ladder" data-options="adoption_ladder"></select>
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label>Current Status</label>
                <select name="current_status" data-options="current_status"></select>
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label>月病人量</label>
                <input type="number" name="monthly_patient_volume" min="0" class="calc-input">
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label>Severe asthma P't %</label>
                <input type="number" name="severe_asthma_pct" min="0" max="100" step="0.1" class="calc-input">
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label>Severe asthma P't No.（自動換算）</label>
                <input type="text" id="severe_asthma_no_display" class="readonly-field" readonly>
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label>Xolair P't %</label>
                <input type="number" name="xolair_pct" min="0" max="100" step="0.1" class="calc-input">
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label>Xolair P't No.（自動換算）</label>
                <input type="text" id="xolair_no_display" class="readonly-field" readonly>
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label>monthly call No</label>
                <input type="number" name="monthly_call_no" min="0">
              </div>
              <div class="field full">
                <label>Competitor Tracking（病人數）</label>
                <div class="form-grid">
                  <div class="field"><label>Dupixent</label><input type="number" name="dupixent_no" min="0"></div>
                  <div class="field"><label>Fasenra</label><input type="number" name="fasenra_no" min="0"></div>
                  <div class="field"><label>Nucala</label><input type="number" name="nucala_no" min="0"></div>
                  <div class="field"><label>Tezspire</label><input type="number" name="tezspire_no" min="0"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="field full">
                <label>competitor activity</label>
                <textarea name="competitor_activity" rows="2"></textarea>
              </div>
              <div class="field full">
                <label>nurse support</label>
                <textarea name="nurse_support" rows="2"></textarea>
              </div>
              <div class="field full">
                <label>Key barriers</label>
                <textarea name="key_barriers" rows="2"></textarea>
              </div>
              <div class="field full">
                <label>Objectives</label>
                <textarea name="objectives" rows="2"></textarea>
              </div>
              <div class="field full">
                <label>Action Plan</label>
                <textarea name="action_plan" rows="3"></textarea>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-top:1rem;">
              <button type="submit">儲存</button>
              <span class="save-status" id="saveStatus"></span>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
        <div class="card" id="emptyState">
          <p style="color:#6b7684;">請從左側選擇一位客戶/醫師以填寫或編輯紀錄。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <script src="/js/psr.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
